author: Disney
description:
The worlds of Disney are filled to the brim with whimsy and wonder—and sometimes, things that are a little, well… weird!

Join our hosts Becky Cline (Director, Walt Disney Archives) and Bret Iwan (Artist and Official Voice of Mickey Mouse) as they share some of the more unusual discoveries from within the many collections of the Walt Disney Archives!

We invite you to join us for the third installment of our new monthly virtual event series in the D23 Gold Theater; Thursday, March 27, 2025, at 5 p.m. PT / 8 p.m. ET.
